{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_battle02","nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"As match day inched closer and closer towards us,@the team's moves also grew more and more refined…","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300201}],"nameCenter":"Natsuki","narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[bgEffect:shakeSmall]Third base!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":300201}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":302901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Masara","textCenter":"…![flashEffect:flashWhite1]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:3223_move_l]*Pomph*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":300201,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Natsuki","narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[chara:300201:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Nice play!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300201,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Natsuki","textCenter":"You're really moving like a kickballer now!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollIn"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[bgEffect:shakeSmall]Yaaah!","turnChangeOut":"rollOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":301601}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:3222_move]*Thwack*"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Right down the middle of right-center field.@Very clean."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"[chara:800300:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]And Awane-senpai scores a triple!@Nice work!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_24012.jpg","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.3},{"autoTurnLast":2.6,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.2},{"autoTurnLast":1.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"And then, at last…@It was the day of the tournament finals.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"narration":"There are four teams still in the race,@which means the first match is our semifinal!@And whichever teams win their semifinals@will continue on to the final, or so it goes."},{"chara":[{"id":302950}],"nameLeft":"Masara","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"So essentially… Win twice, and you take the@tournament home."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"*Giggle* You make it sound so simple.@But yes, exactly!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":302950}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"By the luck of the draw, we dodged the six-time@returning champion team for the semifinals.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narration":"And so, it was finally time for the game."},{"bgm":"bgm01_battle07","chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameCenter":"","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Our opponents this time got past the prelims@with a seven-zero score… They're pretty good."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801000}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800201,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"We know! We saw that match!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800100}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"But we're not the same team that we were@ten days ago!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800201}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"True, it's almost shocking how much you've@all improved."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah, we're going to win this tournament,"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"and we'll have you listen to our plea, Coach!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Just what do you girls want from me,@I wonder…"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"And now, let the first semifinals game begin!@Play ball!\"","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302950,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"Safe!\"[se:7108_arrivals]","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":302950,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Masara","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":302950}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Nice work, Kagami-senpai!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Our top batter is on base now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"And I'll be next…!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":801000}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.9,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"slideInRightFast","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800203,"motion":0,"pos":1}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"effect":"shake","id":800203}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:3223_move_l]*Pomph*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"id":800300,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"[chara:800300:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]They…caught my ball?!@[chara:800300:lipSynch_0][wait:1][chara:800300:lipSynch_1][chara:800300:mouthOpen_0][chara:800300:cheek_0][chara:800300:face_mtn_ex_020.exp3.json]But even still…!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"effect":"slideOutRightFast","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7108_arrivals]*Sprint*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":301650,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Safe! Good infield kick!"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"She's been practicing to start running right@after kicking, and it shows."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"…You're up next, Miss Awane.@Now, here's what you're going to do."},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"Our intensive training worked;@the team became stronger than it ever was.@That, together with our coach's excellent calls,@kept us in the lead for the whole game…","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"And that's the game, 6 to 3!\"","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301650,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kokoro","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"[chara:301650:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Yes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Masara","textRight":"…And into the finals we go."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":160.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story05","nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"Next up was the second game of the semifinals.@As we watched from the bleachers, the six-time@champion team entered the field to wild cheering.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"And then, to everyone's astonishment,@the match ended with…"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"And that's the game, 10 to 0…@First inning run-rule!\"","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Murmur...*","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800100,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameRight":"","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"That was just one inning…!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302950,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"id":800100,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameLeft":"Masara","textLeft":"Faster than in the prelims, even. For a mere@semifinal game, they've certainly tried hard."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":302950},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800100}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800301,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Urk… They're so strong…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"…Their defense is rock-solid, and their kicks@are powerful but still precise."},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"To be honest, our team doesn't stand a chance@against them head-on."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800100}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"But we need to win this!"},{"chara":[{"id":800100}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Otherwise, we can't ask you to play for Japan@again…"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"[chara:800300:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Hey, we're not supposed to tell her that yet…"},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800100},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"…Huh? What did you just say?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"And there, it happened: right before the final game,@the coach learned of the plea that was supposed@to stay secret until the team won."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"So, if you won, you were going to…"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah… "},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"We wanted to ask you to go back to baseball…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"And that was why you were practicing@so much…?"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah…"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"It just doesn't feel right for us to see you out@of the Japan team's uniform."},{"autoTurnLast":0.25,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":801000}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301650,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":302950,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":2}]